---
By: Irving C. Cooper
Locus:
  Page: 289
  Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Life is a gift from God
---
Just as a child goes to school day after day, learning lessons, gathering
experiences and passing from grade to grade, so do we in our greater soul-
life come here to earth many times, learning lessons, gathering experience,
and passing from one social grade to another.
